  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      DHEA supplementation has been used in women with infertility and diminished ovarian reserve.
      There is a small report in 5 women with POF that benefited from the use of DHEA over several
      months. The investigators aim to evaluate further the use of DHEA in women with Premature
      ovarian failure (POF).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
